\begin_layout Title
Clock synchronization
\end_layout

\begin_layout Author
Dario Brazzi, Francesco Pegoraro
\end_layout

\begin_layout Date
February 19, 2013
\end_layout

\begin_layout Abstract
Implement a clock synchronization primitive.
 Choose the strategy that you think best to synchronize the clock of a requestin
g machine against that of a reference (server) machine.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Abstract
In Java implement a library that offers the required functionality and a
 test application that uses this library to synchronize the clocks of a
 group of machines against a reference one.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Part
Problem description
\end_layout

